      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and will require significant work to become roadworthy again. The exterior shows extensive rust on the body panels and the paint is severely faded and peeling in several areas. Mechanically, the engine has trouble starting and there are noticeable leaks that need immediate attention from a mechanic. The interior is heavily worn with tears in the upholstery, making this car best suited as a major restoration project or a source for spare parts.",
